Postcodes

Postcode list for Trafford and Greater Manchester by LA, Ward, MSOA and LSOA with centroids. Trafford file also contains localities.

Metadata

Source Publisher Time period Geography Licence Attribution Last updated
ONS Open Geography Portal Office for National Statistics (ONS) 2024-05-23 Point data OGL v3.0 ONS postcode products (derived from Code-Point Open) are subject to the Open Government Licence. 2024-05-30

Preview

Sort, filter and export a selection of the data using the table. Postcodes for a particular ward within Greater Manchester can also be downloaded via our dedicated Postcode Loader app. These are queried from the API provided by the Office for National Statistics so is always the latest data available.

Pre-processing

The R script used to process the data can be adapted to other areas. For information about R visit the CRAN website.
